##### Vscode -  easily indetifying unsaved files

1. Unsaved files open in vscode will have:

    - a white dot after the file name in the **Editor Tab**. *- red ring*

    - a white dot before the file name in the **Open Editors** section of the *Explorer*. *- red ring*

